⎕VER
⍝ ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
⍝ MARPLE Demo 5: File I/O on Pico
⍝ ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

⍝ ── Write a file ──
'Hello from MARPLE on Pico!' ⎕NWRITE '/test.txt'

⍝ ── Read it back ──
⎕NREAD '/test.txt'

⍝ ── Write and read numeric data as text ──
(⍕⍳10) ⎕NWRITE '/nums.txt'
⎕NREAD '/nums.txt'

⍝ ── Check existence ──
⎕NEXISTS '/test.txt'

⍝ ── Clean up ──
⎕NDELETE '/test.txt'
⎕NDELETE '/nums.txt'
